6679static void
6680handle_scale_factor_changed (GObject *object,
6681 GParamSpec *pspec,
6682 gpointer user_data)
6683{
6684 invalidate_labels (CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (object));
6685 caja_icon_container_request_update_all (CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (object));
6686}
6687
6688static int text_ellipsis_limits[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_N_ENTRIES];
6689static int desktop_text_ellipsis_limit;
6690
6691static gboolean
6692get_text_ellipsis_limit_for_zoom (char **strs,
6693 const char *zoom_level,
6694 int *limit)
6695{
6696 char *str;
6697 gboolean success;
6698
6699 success = FALSE;
6700
6701 /* default */
6702 *limit = 3;
6703
6704 if (zoom_level != NULL)
6705 {
6706 str = g_strdup_printf ("%s:%%d", zoom_level);
6707 }
6708 else
6709 {
6710 str = g_strdup ("%d");
6711 }
6712
6713 if (strs != NULL)
6714 {
6715 char **p;
6716
6717 for (p = strs; *p != NULL; p++)
6718 {
6719 if (sscanf (*p, str, limit))
6720 {
6721 success = TRUE;
6722 }
6723 }
6724 }
6725
6726 g_free (str);
6727
6728 return success;
6729}
6730
6731static const char * zoom_level_names[] = {
6732 "smallest",
6733 "smaller",
6734 "small",
6735 "standard",
6736 "large",
6737 "larger",
6738 "largest"
6739};
6740
6741static void
6742text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback (gpointer callback_data)
6743{
6744 char **pref;
6745 unsigned int i;
6746 int one_limit;
6747
6748 pref = g_settings_get_strv (caja_icon_view_preferences, CAJA_PREFERENCES_ICON_VIEW_TEXT_ELLIPSIS_LIMIT);
6749
6750 /* set default */
6751 get_text_ellipsis_limit_for_zoom (pref, NULL, &one_limit);
6752 for (i = 0; i < CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_N_ENTRIES; i++)
6753 {
6754 text_ellipsis_limits[i] = one_limit;
6755 }
6756
6757 /* override for each zoom level */
6758 for (i = 0; i < G_N_ELEMENTS(zoom_level_names); i++) {
6759 if (get_text_ellipsis_limit_for_zoom (pref,
6760 zoom_level_names[i],
6761 &one_limit)) {
6762 text_ellipsis_limits[i] = one_limit;
6763 }
6764 }
6765
6766 g_strfreev (pref);
6767}
6768
6769static void
6770desktop_text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback (gpointer callback_data)
6771{
6772 int pref;
6773
6774 pref = g_settings_get_int (caja_desktop_preferences, CAJA_PREFERENCES_DESKTOP_TEXT_ELLIPSIS_LIMIT);
6775 desktop_text_ellipsis_limit = pref;
6776}
6777
6778static void
6779caja_icon_container_init (CajaIconContainer *container)
6780{
6781 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
6782 EelBackground *background;
6783 static gboolean setup_prefs = FALSE;
6784
6785 details = g_new0 (CajaIconContainerDetails, 1);
6786
6787 details->icon_set = g_hash_table_new (g_direct_hash, g_direct_equal);
6788 details->layout_timestamp = UNDEFINED_TIME;
6789
6790 details->zoom_level = CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_STANDARD;
6791
6792 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_SMALLEST] = -2 * PANGO_SCALE;
6793 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_SMALLER] = -2 * PANGO_SCALE;
6794 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_SMALL] = -0 * PANGO_SCALE;
6795 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_STANDARD] = 0 * PANGO_SCALE;
6796 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGE] = 0 * PANGO_SCALE;
6797 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGER] = 0 * PANGO_SCALE;
6798 details->font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGEST] = 0 * PANGO_SCALE;
6799
6800 container->details = details;
6801
6802 /* when the background changes, we must set up the label text color */
6803 background = eel_get_widget_background (GTK_WIDGET (container));
6804
6805 g_signal_connect (container, "focus-in-event",
6806 G_CALLBACK (handle_focus_in_event), NULL);
6807 g_signal_connect (container, "focus-out-event",
6808 G_CALLBACK (handle_focus_out_event), NULL);
6809
6810 g_signal_connect (container, "notify::scale-factor",
6811 G_CALLBACK (handle_scale_factor_changed), NULL);
6812
6813 eel_background_set_use_base (background, TRUE);
6814
6815 if (!setup_prefs)
6816 {
6817 g_signal_connect_swapped (caja_icon_view_preferences,
6818 "changed::" CAJA_PREFERENCES_ICON_VIEW_TEXT_ELLIPSIS_LIMIT,
6819 G_CALLBACK (text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback),
6820 NULL);
6821 text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback (NULL);
6822
6823 g_signal_connect_swapped (caja_icon_view_preferences,
6824 "changed::" CAJA_PREFERENCES_DESKTOP_TEXT_ELLIPSIS_LIMIT,
6825 G_CALLBACK (desktop_text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback),
6826 NULL);
6827 desktop_text_ellipsis_limit_changed_callback (NULL);
6828
6829 setup_prefs = TRUE;
6830 }
6831}
6832
6833typedef struct
6834{
6835 CajaIconContainer *container;
6836 GdkEventButton *event;
6837} ContextMenuParameters;
6838
6839static gboolean
6840handle_icon_double_click (CajaIconContainer *container,
6841 CajaIcon *icon,
6842 GdkEventButton *event)
6843{
6844 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
6845
6846 if (event->button != DRAG_BUTTON)
6847 {
6848 return FALSE;
6849 }
6850
6851 details = container->details;
6852
6853 if (!details->single_click_mode &&
6854 clicked_within_double_click_interval (container) &&
6855 details->double_click_icon[0] == details->double_click_icon[1] &&
6856 details->double_click_button[0] == details->double_click_button[1])
6857 {
6858 if (!button_event_modifies_selection (event))
6859 {
6860 activate_selected_items (container);
6861 return TRUE;
6862 }
6863 else if ((event->state & GDK_CONTROL_MASK) == 0 &&
6864 (event->state & GDK_SHIFT_MASK) != 0)
6865 {
6866 activate_selected_items_alternate (container, icon);
6867 return TRUE;
6868 }
6869 }
6870
6871 return FALSE;
6872}
6873
6874/* CajaIcon event handling. */
6875
6876/* Conceptually, pressing button 1 together with CTRL or SHIFT toggles
6877 * selection of a single icon without affecting the other icons;
6878 * without CTRL or SHIFT, it selects a single icon and un-selects all
6879 * the other icons. But in this latter case, the de-selection should
6880 * only happen when the button is released if the icon is already
6881 * selected, because the user might select multiple icons and drag all
6882 * of them by doing a simple click-drag.
6883*/
6884
6885static gboolean
6886handle_icon_button_press (CajaIconContainer *container,
6887 CajaIcon *icon,
6888 GdkEventButton *event)
6889{
6890 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
6891
6892 details = container->details;
6893
6894 if (event->type == GDK_2BUTTON_PRESS || event->type == GDK_3BUTTON_PRESS)
6895 {
6896 return TRUE;
6897 }
6898
6899 if (event->button != DRAG_BUTTON
6900 && event->button != CONTEXTUAL_MENU_BUTTON
6901 && event->button != DRAG_MENU_BUTTON)
6902 {
6903 return TRUE;
6904 }
6905
6906 if ((event->button == DRAG_BUTTON) &&
6907 event->type == GDK_BUTTON_PRESS)
6908 {
6909 /* The next double click has to be on this icon */
6910 details->double_click_icon[1] = details->double_click_icon[0];
6911 details->double_click_icon[0] = icon;
6912
6913 details->double_click_button[1] = details->double_click_button[0];
6914 details->double_click_button[0] = event->button;
6915 }
6916
6917 if (handle_icon_double_click (container, icon, event))
6918 {
6919 /* Double clicking does not trigger a D&D action. */
6920 details->drag_button = 0;
6921 details->drag_icon = NULL;
6922 return TRUE;
6923 }
6924
6925 if (event->button == DRAG_BUTTON
6926 || event->button == DRAG_MENU_BUTTON)
6927 {
6928 details->drag_button = event->button;
6929 details->drag_icon = icon;
6930 details->drag_x = event->x;
6931 details->drag_y = event->y;
6932 details->drag_state = DRAG_STATE_MOVE_OR_COPY;
6933 details->drag_started = FALSE;
6934
6935 /* Check to see if this is a click on the stretch handles.
6936 * If so, it won't modify the selection.
6937 */
6938 if (icon == container->details->stretch_icon)
6939 {
6940 if (start_stretching (container, (GdkEvent *)event))
6941 {
6942 return TRUE;
6943 }
6944 }
6945 }
6946
6947 /* Modify the selection as appropriate. Selection is modified
6948 * the same way for contextual menu as it would be without.
6949 */
6950 details->icon_selected_on_button_down = icon->is_selected;
6951
6952 if ((event->button == DRAG_BUTTON || event->button == MIDDLE_BUTTON) &&
6953 (event->state & GDK_SHIFT_MASK) != 0)
6954 {
6955 CajaIcon *start_icon;
6956
6957 start_icon = details->range_selection_base_icon;
6958 if (start_icon == NULL || !start_icon->is_selected)
6959 {
6960 start_icon = icon;
6961 details->range_selection_base_icon = icon;
6962 }
6963 if (select_range (container, start_icon, icon,
6964 (event->state & GDK_CONTROL_MASK) == 0))
6965 {
6966 g_signal_emit (container,
6967 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
6968 }
6969 }
6970 else if (!details->icon_selected_on_button_down)
6971 {
6972 details->range_selection_base_icon = icon;
6973 if (button_event_modifies_selection (event))
6974 {
6975 icon_toggle_selected (container, icon);
6976 g_signal_emit (container,
6977 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
6978 }
6979 else
6980 {
6981 select_one_unselect_others (container, icon);
6982 g_signal_emit (container,
6983 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
6984 }
6985 }
6986
6987 if (event->button == CONTEXTUAL_MENU_BUTTON)
6988 {
6989 g_signal_emit (container,
6990 signals[CONTEXT_CLICK_SELECTION], 0,
6991 event);
6992 }
6993
6994 return TRUE;
6995}
6996
6997static int
6998item_event_callback (EelCanvasItem *item,
6999 GdkEvent *event,
7000 gpointer data)
7001{
7002 CajaIconContainer *container;
7003 CajaIcon *icon;
7004
7005 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (data);
7006
7007 icon = CAJA_ICON_CANVAS_ITEM (item)->user_data;
7008 g_assert (icon != NULL);
7009
7010 switch (event->type)
7011 {
7012 case GDK_BUTTON_PRESS:
7013 if (handle_icon_button_press (container, icon, &event->button))
7014 {
7015 /* Stop the event from being passed along further. Returning
7016 * TRUE ain't enough.
7017 */
7018 return TRUE;
7019 }
7020 return FALSE;
7021 default:
7022 return FALSE;
7023 }
7024}
7025
7026GtkWidget *
7027caja_icon_container_new (void)
7028{
7029 return gtk_widget_new (CAJA_TYPE_ICON_CONTAINER, NULL);
7030}
7031
7032/* Clear all of the icons in the container. */
7033void
7034caja_icon_container_clear (CajaIconContainer *container)
7035{
7036 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
7037 GList *p;
7038 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
7039
7040 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
7041
7042 details = container->details;
7043 details->layout_timestamp = UNDEFINED_TIME;
7044 details->store_layout_timestamps_when_finishing_new_icons = FALSE;
7045
7046 if (details->icons == NULL)
7047 {
7048 return;
7049 }
7050
7051 end_renaming_mode (container, TRUE);
7052
7053 clear_keyboard_focus (container);
7054 clear_keyboard_rubberband_start (container);
7055 unschedule_keyboard_icon_reveal (container);
7056 set_pending_icon_to_reveal (container, NULL);
7057 details->stretch_icon = NULL;
7058 details->drop_target = NULL;
7059
7060 for (p = details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
7061 {
7062 icon = p->data;
7063 if (icon->is_monitored)
7064 {
7065 caja_icon_container_stop_monitor_top_left (container,
7066 icon->data,
7067 icon);
7068 }
7069 icon_free (p->data);
7070 }
7071 g_list_free (details->icons);
7072 details->icons = NULL;
7073 g_list_free (details->new_icons);
7074 details->new_icons = NULL;
7075
7076 g_hash_table_destroy (details->icon_set);
7077 details->icon_set = g_hash_table_new (g_direct_hash, g_direct_equal);
7078
7079 caja_icon_container_update_scroll_region (container);
7080}
7081
7082gboolean
7083caja_icon_container_is_empty (CajaIconContainer *container)
7084{
7085 return container->details->icons == NULL;
7086}
7087
7088CajaIconData *
7089caja_icon_container_get_first_visible_icon (CajaIconContainer *container)
7090{
7091 GList *l;
7092 CajaIcon *icon, *best_icon;
7093 double x, y;
7094 double x1, y1, x2, y2;
7095 double *pos, best_pos;
7096 double hadj_v, vadj_v, h_page_size;
7097 gboolean better_icon;
7098 gboolean compare_lt;
7099
7100 hadj_v = gtk_adjustment_get_value (gtk_scrollable_get_hadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container)));
7101 vadj_v = gtk_adjustment_get_value (gtk_scrollable_get_vadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container)));
7102 h_page_size = gtk_adjustment_get_page_size (gtk_scrollable_get_hadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container)));
7103
7104 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_rtl (container))
7105 {
7106 x = hadj_v + h_page_size - ICON_PAD_LEFT - 1;
7107 y = vadj_v;
7108 }
7109 else
7110 {
7111 x = hadj_v;
7112 y = vadj_v;
7113 }
7114
7115 eel_canvas_c2w (EEL_CANVAS (container),
7116 x, y,
7117 &x, &y);
7118
7119 l = container->details->icons;
7120 best_icon = NULL;
7121 best_pos = 0;
7122 while (l != NULL)
7123 {
7124 icon = l->data;
7125
7126 if (icon_is_positioned (icon))
7127 {
7128 eel_canvas_item_get_bounds (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item),
7129 &x1, &y1, &x2, &y2);
7130
7131 compare_lt = FALSE;
7132 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container))
7133 {
7134 pos = &x1;
7135 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_rtl (container))
7136 {
7137 compare_lt = TRUE;
7138 better_icon = x1 < x + ICON_PAD_LEFT;
7139 }
7140 else
7141 {
7142 better_icon = x2 > x + ICON_PAD_LEFT;
7143 }
7144 }
7145 else
7146 {
7147 pos = &y1;
7148 better_icon = y2 > y + ICON_PAD_TOP;
7149 }
7150 if (better_icon)
7151 {
7152 if (best_icon == NULL)
7153 {
7154 better_icon = TRUE;
7155 }
7156 else if (compare_lt)
7157 {
7158 better_icon = best_pos < *pos;
7159 }
7160 else
7161 {
7162 better_icon = best_pos > *pos;
7163 }
7164
7165 if (better_icon)
7166 {
7167 best_icon = icon;
7168 best_pos = *pos;
7169 }
7170 }
7171 }
7172
7173 l = l->next;
7174 }
7175
7176 return best_icon ? best_icon->data : NULL;
7177}
7178
7179/* puts the icon at the top of the screen */
7180void
7181caja_icon_container_scroll_to_icon (CajaIconContainer *container,
7182 CajaIconData *data)
7183{
7184 GList *l;
7185 GtkAdjustment *hadj, *vadj;
7186 EelIRect bounds;
7187 GtkAllocation allocation;
7188 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
7189
7190 hadj = gtk_scrollable_get_hadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container));
7191 vadj = gtk_scrollable_get_vadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container));
7192 gtk_widget_get_allocation (GTK_WIDGET (container), &allocation);
7193
7194 /* We need to force a relayout now if there are updates queued
7195 * since we need the final positions */
7196 caja_icon_container_layout_now (container);
7197
7198 l = container->details->icons;
7199 while (l != NULL) {
7200 icon = l->data;
7201
7202 if (icon->data == data &&
7203 icon_is_positioned (icon)) {
7204
7205 if (caja_icon_container_is_auto_layout (container)) {
7206 /* ensure that we reveal the entire row/column */
7207 icon_get_row_and_column_bounds (container, icon, &bounds, TRUE);
7208 } else {
7209 item_get_canvas_bounds (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item), &bounds, TRUE);
7210 }
7211
7212 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container)) {
7213 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_rtl (container)) {
7214 gtk_adjustment_set_value (hadj, bounds.x1 - allocation.width);
7215 } else {
7216 gtk_adjustment_set_value (hadj, bounds.x0);
7217 }
7218 } else {
7219 gtk_adjustment_set_value (vadj, bounds.y0);
7220 }
7221 }
7222
7223 l = l->next;
7224 }
7225}
7226
7227/* Call a function for all the icons. */
7228typedef struct
7229{
7230 CajaIconCallback callback;
7231 gpointer callback_data;
7232} CallbackAndData;
7233
7234static void
7235call_icon_callback (gpointer data, gpointer callback_data)
7236{
7237 CajaIcon *icon;
7238 CallbackAndData *callback_and_data;
7239
7240 icon = data;
7241 callback_and_data = callback_data;
7242 (* callback_and_data->callback) (icon->data, callback_and_data->callback_data);
7243}
7244
7245void
7246caja_icon_container_for_each (CajaIconContainer *container,
7247 CajaIconCallback callback,
7248 gpointer callback_data)
7249{
7250 CallbackAndData callback_and_data;
7251
7252 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
7253
7254 callback_and_data.callback = callback;
7255 callback_and_data.callback_data = callback_data;
7256
7257 g_list_foreach (container->details->icons,
7258 call_icon_callback, &callback_and_data);
7259}
7260
7261static int
7262selection_changed_at_idle_callback (gpointer data)
7263{
7264 CajaIconContainer *container;
7265
7266 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (data);
7267
7268 g_signal_emit (container,
7269 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
7270
7271 container->details->selection_changed_id = 0;
7272 return FALSE;
7273}
7274
7275/* utility routine to remove a single icon from the container */
7276
7277static void
7278icon_destroy (CajaIconContainer *container,
7279 CajaIcon *icon)
7280{
7281 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
7282 gboolean was_selected;
7283 CajaIcon *icon_to_focus;
7284 GList *item;
7285
7286 details = container->details;
7287
7288 item = g_list_find (details->icons, icon);
7289 item = item->next ? item->next : item->prev;
7290 icon_to_focus = (item != NULL) ? item->data : NULL;
7291
7292 details->icons = g_list_remove (details->icons, icon);
7293 details->new_icons = g_list_remove (details->new_icons, icon);
7294 g_hash_table_remove (details->icon_set, icon->data);
7295
7296 was_selected = icon->is_selected;
7297
7298 if (details->keyboard_focus == icon ||
7299 details->keyboard_focus == NULL)
7300 {
7301 if (icon_to_focus != NULL)
7302 {
7303 set_keyboard_focus (container, icon_to_focus);
7304 }
7305 else
7306 {
7307 clear_keyboard_focus (container);
7308 }
7309 }
7310
7311 if (details->keyboard_rubberband_start == icon)
7312 {
7313 clear_keyboard_rubberband_start (container);
7314 }
7315
7316 if (details->keyboard_icon_to_reveal == icon)
7317 {
7318 unschedule_keyboard_icon_reveal (container);
7319 }
7320 if (details->drag_icon == icon)
7321 {
7322 clear_drag_state (container);
7323 }
7324 if (details->drop_target == icon)
7325 {
7326 details->drop_target = NULL;
7327 }
7328 if (details->range_selection_base_icon == icon)
7329 {
7330 details->range_selection_base_icon = NULL;
7331 }
7332 if (details->pending_icon_to_reveal == icon)
7333 {
7334 set_pending_icon_to_reveal (container, NULL);
7335 }
7336 if (details->stretch_icon == icon)
7337 {
7338 details->stretch_icon = NULL;
7339 }
7340
7341 if (icon->is_monitored)
7342 {
7343 caja_icon_container_stop_monitor_top_left (container,
7344 icon->data,
7345 icon);
7346 }
7347 icon_free (icon);
7348
7349 if (was_selected)
7350 {
7351 /* Coalesce multiple removals causing multiple selection_changed events */
7352 details->selection_changed_id = g_idle_add (selection_changed_at_idle_callback, container);
7353 }
7354}
7355
7356/* activate any selected items in the container */
7357static void
7358activate_selected_items (CajaIconContainer *container)
7359{
7360 GList *selection;
7361
7362 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
7363
7364 selection = caja_icon_container_get_selection (container);
7365 if (selection != NULL)
7366 {
7367 g_signal_emit (container,
7368 signals[ACTIVATE], 0,
7369 selection);
7370 }
7371 g_list_free (selection);
7372}
7373
7374static void
7375activate_selected_items_alternate (CajaIconContainer *container,
7376 CajaIcon *icon)
7377{
7378 GList *selection;
7379
7380 g_assert (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
7381
7382 if (icon != NULL)
7383 {
7384 selection = g_list_prepend (NULL, icon->data);
7385 }
7386 else
7387 {
7388 selection = caja_icon_container_get_selection (container);
7389 }
7390 if (selection != NULL)
7391 {
7392 g_signal_emit (container,
7393 signals[ACTIVATE_ALTERNATE], 0,
7394 selection);
7395 }
7396 g_list_free (selection);
7397}

7405 {

7407 }
7408

7410

7496
7497static void
7498caja_icon_container_update_visible_icons (CajaIconContainer *container)
7499{
7500 GtkAdjustment *vadj, *hadj;
7501 double min_y, max_y;
7502 double min_x, max_x;
7503 double x0, y0, x1, y1;
7504 GList *node;
7505 gboolean visible;
7506 GtkAllocation allocation;
7507 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
7508
7509 hadj = gtk_scrollable_get_hadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container));
7510 vadj = gtk_scrollable_get_vadjustment (GTK_SCROLLABLE (container));
7511 gtk_widget_get_allocation (GTK_WIDGET (container), &allocation);
7512
7513 min_x = gtk_adjustment_get_value (hadj);
7514 max_x = min_x + allocation.width;
7515
7516 min_y = gtk_adjustment_get_value (vadj);
7517 max_y = min_y + allocation.height;
7518
7519 eel_canvas_c2w (EEL_CANVAS (container),
7520 min_x, min_y, &min_x, &min_y);
7521 eel_canvas_c2w (EEL_CANVAS (container),
7522 max_x, max_y, &max_x, &max_y);
7523
7524 /* Do the iteration in reverse to get the render-order from top to
7525 * bottom for the prioritized thumbnails.
7526 */
7527 for (node = g_list_last (container->details->icons); node != NULL; node = node->prev)
7528 {
7529 icon = node->data;
7530
7531 if (icon_is_positioned (icon))
7532 {
7533 eel_canvas_item_get_bounds (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item),
7534 &x0,
7535 &y0,
7536 &x1,
7537 &y1);
7538 eel_canvas_item_i2w (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item)->parent,
7539 &x0,
7540 &y0);
7541 eel_canvas_item_i2w (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item)->parent,
7542 &x1,
7543 &y1);
7544
7545 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container))
7546 {
7547 visible = x1 >= min_x && x0 <= max_x;
7548 }
7549 else
7550 {
7551 visible = y1 >= min_y && y0 <= max_y;
7552 }
7553
7554 if (visible)
7555 {
7556 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_is_visible (icon->item, TRUE);
7557 caja_icon_container_prioritize_thumbnailing (container,
7558 icon);
7559 }
7560 else
7561 {
7562 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_is_visible (icon->item, FALSE);
7563 }
7564 }
7565 }
7566}
7567
7568static void
7569handle_vadjustment_changed (GtkAdjustment *adjustment,
7570 CajaIconContainer *container)
7571{
7572 if (!caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container))
7573 {
7574 caja_icon_container_update_visible_icons (container);
7575 }
7576}
7577
7578static void
7579handle_hadjustment_changed (GtkAdjustment *adjustment,
7580 CajaIconContainer *container)
7581{
7582 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container))
7583 {
7584 caja_icon_container_update_visible_icons (container);
7585 }
7586}
7587
7588void
7589caja_icon_container_update_icon (CajaIconContainer *container,
7590 CajaIcon *icon)
7591{
7592 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
7593 guint icon_size;
7594 guint min_image_size, max_image_size;
7595 CajaIconInfo *icon_info;
7596 GdkPoint *attach_points;
7597 int n_attach_points;
7598 gboolean has_embedded_text_rect;
7599 GdkPixbuf *pixbuf;
7600 GList *emblem_pixbufs;
7601 char *editable_text, *additional_text;
7602 char *embedded_text;
7603 GdkRectangle embedded_text_rect;
7604 gboolean large_embedded_text;
7605 gboolean embedded_text_needs_loading;
7606 gboolean has_open_window;
7607
7608 if (icon == NULL)
7609 {
7610 return;
7611 }
7612
7613 details = container->details;
7614
7615 /* compute the maximum size based on the scale factor */
7616 min_image_size = MINIMUM_IMAGE_SIZE * EEL_CANVAS (container)->pixels_per_unit;
7617 max_image_size = MAX (MAXIMUM_IMAGE_SIZE * EEL_CANVAS (container)->pixels_per_unit, CAJA_ICON_MAXIMUM_SIZE);
7618
7619 /* Get the appropriate images for the file. */
7620 if (container->details->forced_icon_size > 0)
7621 {
7622 icon_size = container->details->forced_icon_size;
7623 }
7624 else
7625 {
7626 icon_get_size (container, icon, &icon_size);
7627 }
7628
7629 icon_size = MAX (icon_size, min_image_size);
7630 icon_size = MIN (icon_size, max_image_size);
7631
7632 /* Get the icons. */
7633 emblem_pixbufs = NULL;
7634 embedded_text = NULL;
7635 large_embedded_text = icon_size > ICON_SIZE_FOR_LARGE_EMBEDDED_TEXT;
7636 icon_info = caja_icon_container_get_icon_images (container, icon->data, icon_size,
7637 &emblem_pixbufs,
7638 &embedded_text,
7639 icon == details->drop_target,
7640 large_embedded_text, &embedded_text_needs_loading,
7641 &has_open_window);
7642
7643 if (container->details->forced_icon_size > 0)
7644 pixbuf = caja_icon_info_get_pixbuf_at_size (icon_info, icon_size);
7645 else
7646 pixbuf = caja_icon_info_get_pixbuf (icon_info);
7647 caja_icon_info_get_attach_points (icon_info, &attach_points, &n_attach_points);
7648 has_embedded_text_rect = caja_icon_info_get_embedded_rect (icon_info,
7649 &embedded_text_rect);
7650
7651 if (has_embedded_text_rect && embedded_text_needs_loading)
7652 {
7653 icon->is_monitored = TRUE;
7654 caja_icon_container_start_monitor_top_left (container, icon->data, icon, large_embedded_text);
7655 }
7656
7657 caja_icon_container_get_icon_text (container,
7658 icon->data,
7659 &editable_text,
7660 &additional_text,
7661 FALSE);
7662
7663 /* If name of icon being renamed was changed from elsewhere, end renaming mode.
7664 * Alternatively, we could replace the characters in the editable text widget
7665 * with the new name, but that could cause timing problems if the user just
7666 * happened to be typing at that moment.
7667 */
7668 if (icon == get_icon_being_renamed (container) &&
7669 g_strcmp0 (editable_text,
7670 caja_icon_canvas_item_get_editable_text (icon->item)) != 0)
7671 {
7672 end_renaming_mode (container, FALSE);
7673 }
7674
7675 eel_canvas_item_set (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item),
7676 "editable_text", editable_text,
7677 "additional_text", additional_text,
7678 "highlighted_for_drop", icon == details->drop_target,
7679 NULL);
7680
7681 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_image (icon->item, pixbuf);
7682 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_attach_points (icon->item, attach_points, n_attach_points);
7683 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_emblems (icon->item, emblem_pixbufs);
7684 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_embedded_text_rect (icon->item, &embedded_text_rect);
7685 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_embedded_text (icon->item, embedded_text);
7686
7687 /* Let the pixbufs go. */
7688 g_object_unref (pixbuf);
7689 g_list_free_full (emblem_pixbufs, g_object_unref);
7690
7691 g_free (editable_text);
7692 g_free (additional_text);
7693
7694 g_object_unref (icon_info);
7695}
7696
7697static gboolean
7698assign_icon_position (CajaIconContainer *container,
7699 CajaIcon *icon)
7700{
7701 gboolean have_stored_position;
7702 CajaIconPosition position;
7703
7704 /* Get the stored position. */
7705 have_stored_position = FALSE;
7706 position.scale = 1.0;
7707 g_signal_emit (container,
7708 signals[GET_STORED_ICON_POSITION], 0,
7709 icon->data,
7710 &position,
7711 &have_stored_position);
7712 icon->scale = position.scale;
7713 if (!container->details->auto_layout)
7714 {
7715 if (have_stored_position)
7716 {
7717 icon_set_position (icon, position.x, position.y);
7718 icon->saved_ltr_x = icon->x;
7719 }
7720 else
7721 {
7722 return FALSE;
7723 }
7724 }
7725 return TRUE;
7726}
7727
7728static void
7729finish_adding_new_icons (CajaIconContainer *container)
7730{
7731 GList *p, *new_icons, *no_position_icons, *semi_position_icons;
7732 CajaIcon *icon;
7733 double bottom;
7734
7735 new_icons = container->details->new_icons;
7736 container->details->new_icons = NULL;
7737 container->details->is_populating_container =
7738 g_list_length(new_icons) == g_hash_table_size(container->details->icon_set);
7739
7740 /* Position most icons (not unpositioned manual-layout icons). */
7741 new_icons = g_list_reverse (new_icons);
7742 no_position_icons = semi_position_icons = NULL;
7743 for (p = new_icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
7744 {
7745 icon = p->data;
7746 caja_icon_container_update_icon (container, icon);
7747 if (icon->has_lazy_position)
7748 {
7749 assign_icon_position (container, icon);
7750 semi_position_icons = g_list_prepend (semi_position_icons, icon);
7751 }
7752 else if (!assign_icon_position (container, icon))
7753 {
7754 no_position_icons = g_list_prepend (no_position_icons, icon);
7755 }
7756
7757 eel_canvas_item_show (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item));
7758
7759 g_signal_connect_object (icon->item, "event",
7760 G_CALLBACK (item_event_callback), container, 0);
7761
7762 g_signal_emit (container, signals[ICON_ADDED], 0, icon->data);
7763 }
7764 g_list_free (new_icons);
7765
7766 if (semi_position_icons != NULL)
7767 {
7768 PlacementGrid *grid;
7769 time_t now;
7770 gboolean dummy;
7771
7772 g_assert (!container->details->auto_layout);
7773
7774 semi_position_icons = g_list_reverse (semi_position_icons);
7775
7776 /* This is currently only used on the desktop.
7777 * Thus, we pass FALSE for tight, like lay_down_icons_tblr */
7778 grid = placement_grid_new (container, FALSE);
7779
7780 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
7781 {
7782 icon = p->data;
7783
7784 if (icon_is_positioned (icon) && !icon->has_lazy_position)
7785 {
7786 placement_grid_mark_icon (grid, icon);
7787 }
7788 }
7789
7790 now = time (NULL);
7791
7792 for (p = semi_position_icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
7793 {
7794 CajaIcon *icon;
7795 CajaIconPosition position;
7796 int x, y;
7797
7798 icon = p->data;
7799 x = icon->x;
7800 y = icon->y;
7801
7802 find_empty_location (container, grid,
7803 icon, x, y, &x, &y);
7804
7805 icon_set_position (icon, x, y);
7806
7807 position.x = icon->x;
7808 position.y = icon->y;
7809 position.scale = icon->scale;
7810 placement_grid_mark_icon (grid, icon);
7811 g_signal_emit (container, signals[ICON_POSITION_CHANGED], 0,
7812 icon->data, &position);
7813 g_signal_emit (container, signals[STORE_LAYOUT_TIMESTAMP], 0,
7814 icon->data, &now, &dummy);
7815
7816 /* ensure that next time we run this code, the formerly semi-positioned
7817 * icons are treated as being positioned. */
7818 icon->has_lazy_position = FALSE;
7819 }
7820
7821 placement_grid_free (grid);
7822
7823 g_list_free (semi_position_icons);
7824 }
7825
7826 /* Position the unpositioned manual layout icons. */
7827 if (no_position_icons != NULL)
7828 {
7829 g_assert (!container->details->auto_layout);
7830
7831 sort_icons (container, &no_position_icons);
7832 if (caja_icon_container_get_is_desktop (container))
7833 {
7834 lay_down_icons (container, no_position_icons, CONTAINER_PAD_TOP);
7835 }
7836 else
7837 {
7838 get_all_icon_bounds (container, NULL, NULL, NULL, &bottom, BOUNDS_USAGE_FOR_LAYOUT);
7839 lay_down_icons (container, no_position_icons, bottom + ICON_PAD_BOTTOM);
7840 }
7841 g_list_free (no_position_icons);
7842 }
7843
7844 if (container->details->store_layout_timestamps_when_finishing_new_icons)
7845 {
7846 store_layout_timestamps_now (container);
7847 container->details->store_layout_timestamps_when_finishing_new_icons = FALSE;
7848 }
7849}
7850
7851static gboolean
7852is_old_or_unknown_icon_data (CajaIconContainer *container,
7853 CajaIconData *data)
7854{
7855 time_t timestamp;
7856 gboolean success;
7857
7858 if (container->details->layout_timestamp == UNDEFINED_TIME)
7859 {
7860 /* don't know */
7861 return FALSE;
7862 }
7863
7864 g_signal_emit (container,
7865 signals[GET_STORED_LAYOUT_TIMESTAMP], 0,
7866 data, &timestamp, &success);
7867 return (!success || timestamp < container->details->layout_timestamp);
7868}
7869
7878gboolean
7879caja_icon_container_add (CajaIconContainer *container,
7880 CajaIconData *data)
7881{
7882 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
7883 CajaIcon *icon;
7884 EelCanvasItem *band, *item;
7885
7886 g_return_val_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container), FALSE);
7887 g_return_val_if_fail (data != NULL, FALSE);
7888
7889 details = container->details;
7890
7891 if (g_hash_table_lookup (details->icon_set, data) != NULL)
7892 {
7893 return FALSE;
7894 }
7895
7896 /* Create the new icon, including the canvas item. */
7897 icon = g_new0 (CajaIcon, 1);
7898 icon->data = data;
7899 icon->x = ICON_UNPOSITIONED_VALUE;
7900 icon->y = ICON_UNPOSITIONED_VALUE;
7901
7902 /* Whether the saved icon position should only be used
7903 * if the previous icon position is free. If the position
7904 * is occupied, another position near the last one will
7905 */
7906 icon->has_lazy_position = (is_old_or_unknown_icon_data (container, data) != FALSE);
7907 icon->scale = 1.0;
7908 icon->item = CAJA_ICON_CANVAS_ITEM
7909 (eel_canvas_item_new (EEL_CANVAS_GROUP (EEL_CANVAS (container)->root),
7910 caja_icon_canvas_item_get_type (),
7911 "visible", FALSE,
7912 NULL));
7913 icon->item->user_data = icon;
7914
7915 /* Make sure the icon is under the selection_rectangle */
7916 item = EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item);
7917 band = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (item->canvas)->details->rubberband_info.selection_rectangle;
7918 if (band)
7919 {
7920 eel_canvas_item_send_behind (item, band);
7921 }
7922
7923 /* Put it on both lists. */
7924 details->icons = g_list_prepend (details->icons, icon);
7925 details->new_icons = g_list_prepend (details->new_icons, icon);
7926
7927 g_hash_table_insert (details->icon_set, data, icon);
7928
7929 /* Run an idle function to add the icons. */
7930 schedule_redo_layout (container);
7931
7932 return TRUE;
7933}
7934
7935void
7936caja_icon_container_layout_now (CajaIconContainer *container)
7937{
7938 if (container->details->idle_id != 0)
7939 {
7940 unschedule_redo_layout (container);
7941 redo_layout_internal (container);
7942 }
7943
7944 /* Also need to make sure we're properly resized, for instance
7945 * newly added files may trigger a change in the size allocation and
7946 * thus toggle scrollbars on */
7947 gtk_container_check_resize (GTK_CONTAINER (gtk_widget_get_parent (GTK_WIDGET (container))));
7948}

7957gboolean
7958caja_icon_container_remove (CajaIconContainer *container,
7959 CajaIconData *data)
7960{
7961 CajaIcon *icon;
7962
7963 g_return_val_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container), FALSE);
7964 g_return_val_if_fail (data != NULL, FALSE);
7965
7966 end_renaming_mode (container, FALSE);
7967
7968 icon = g_hash_table_lookup (container->details->icon_set, data);
7969
7970 if (icon == NULL)
7971 {
7972 return FALSE;
7973 }
7974
7975 g_signal_emit (container, signals[ICON_REMOVED], 0, icon);
7976
7977 icon_destroy (container, icon);
7978 schedule_redo_layout (container);
7979
7980 return TRUE;
7981}

8000

8008/* zooming */
8009
8010CajaZoomLevel
8011caja_icon_container_get_zoom_level (CajaIconContainer *container)
8012{
8013 return container->details->zoom_level;
8014}
8015
8016void
8017caja_icon_container_set_zoom_level (CajaIconContainer *container, int new_level)
8018{
8019 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
8020 int pinned_level;
8021 double pixels_per_unit;
8022 guint icon_size;
8023
8024 details = container->details;
8025
8026 end_renaming_mode (container, TRUE);
8027
8028 pinned_level = new_level;
8029 if (pinned_level < CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_SMALLEST)
8030 {
8031 pinned_level = CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_SMALLEST;
8032 }
8033 else if (pinned_level > CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGEST)
8034 {
8035 pinned_level = CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGEST;
8036 }
8037
8038 if (pinned_level == details->zoom_level)
8039 {
8040 return;
8041 }
8042
8043 details->zoom_level = pinned_level;
8044
8045 icon_size = caja_get_icon_size_for_zoom_level (pinned_level);
8046 pixels_per_unit = ((double) icon_size) / ((double) CAJA_ICON_SIZE_STANDARD);
8047 eel_canvas_set_pixels_per_unit (EEL_CANVAS (container), pixels_per_unit);
8048
8049 invalidate_labels (container);
8050 caja_icon_container_request_update_all (container);
8051}
8052
8060void
8061caja_icon_container_request_update_all (CajaIconContainer *container)
8062{
8063 GList *node;
8064 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
8065
8066 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
8067
8068 container->details->is_loading = TRUE;
8069 for (node = container->details->icons; node != NULL; node = node->next)
8070 {
8071 icon = node->data;
8072 caja_icon_container_update_icon (container, icon);
8073 }
8074
8075 /* on manual layout we need to reload icon positions, as that might be
8076 * affected by the view size, zoom, etc. */
8077 if (!container->details->auto_layout)
8078 reload_icon_positions (container, FALSE);
8079
8080 redo_layout (container);
8081 container->details->is_loading = FALSE;
8082}

8183/* Returns an array of GdkPoints of locations of the icons. */
8184static GArray *
8185caja_icon_container_get_icon_locations (CajaIconContainer *container,
8186 GList *icons)
8187{
8188 GArray *result;
8189 GList *node;
8190 int index;
8191
8192 result = g_array_new (FALSE, TRUE, sizeof (GdkPoint));
8193 result = g_array_set_size (result, g_list_length (icons));
8194
8195 for (index = 0, node = icons; node != NULL; index++, node = node->next)
8196 {
8197 g_array_index (result, GdkPoint, index).x =
8198 ((CajaIcon *)node->data)->x;
8199 g_array_index (result, GdkPoint, index).y =
8200 ((CajaIcon *)node->data)->y;
8201 }
8202
8203 return result;
8204}
8205
8212GArray *
8213caja_icon_container_get_selected_icon_locations (CajaIconContainer *container)
8214{
8215 GArray *result;
8216 GList *icons;
8217
8218 g_return_val_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container), NULL);
8219
8220 icons = caja_icon_container_get_selected_icons (container);
8221 result = caja_icon_container_get_icon_locations (container, icons);
8222 g_list_free (icons);
8223
8224 return result;
8225}

8233void
8234caja_icon_container_select_all (CajaIconContainer *container)
8235{
8236 gboolean selection_changed;
8237 GList *p;
8238 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
8239
8240 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
8241
8242 selection_changed = FALSE;
8243
8244 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8245 {
8246 icon = p->data;
8247
8248 selection_changed |= icon_set_selected (container, icon, TRUE);
8249 }
8250
8251 if (selection_changed)
8252 {
8253 g_signal_emit (container,
8254 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
8255 }
8256}
8257
8266void
8267caja_icon_container_set_selection (CajaIconContainer *container,
8268 GList *selection)
8269{
8270 gboolean selection_changed;
8271 GHashTable *hash;
8272 GList *p;
8273 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
8274
8275 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
8276
8277 selection_changed = FALSE;
8278
8279 hash = g_hash_table_new (NULL, NULL);
8280 for (p = selection; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8281 {
8282 g_hash_table_insert (hash, p->data, p->data);
8283 }
8284 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8285 {
8286 icon = p->data;
8287
8288 selection_changed |= icon_set_selected
8289 (container, icon,
8290 g_hash_table_lookup (hash, icon->data) != NULL);
8291 }
8292 g_hash_table_destroy (hash);
8293
8294 if (selection_changed)
8295 {
8296 g_signal_emit (container,
8297 signals[SELECTION_CHANGED], 0);
8298 }
8299}

8358
8368CajaIcon *
8369caja_icon_container_get_icon_by_uri (CajaIconContainer *container,
8370 const char *uri)
8371{
8372 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
8373 GList *p;
8374
8375 /* Eventually, we must avoid searching the entire icon list,
8376 but it's OK for now.
8377 A hash table mapping uri to icon is one possibility.
8378 */
8379
8380 details = container->details;
8381
8382 for (p = details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8383 {
8384 CajaIcon *icon;
8385 char *icon_uri;
8386 gboolean is_match;
8387
8388 icon = p->data;
8389
8390 icon_uri = caja_icon_container_get_icon_uri
8391 (container, icon);
8392 is_match = strcmp (uri, icon_uri) == 0;
8393 g_free (icon_uri);
8394
8395 if (is_match)
8396 {
8397 return icon;
8398 }
8399 }
8400
8401 return NULL;
8402}

8404static CajaIcon *
8405get_nth_selected_icon (CajaIconContainer *container, int index)
8406{
8407 GList *p;
8408 int selection_count;
8409 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
8410
8411 g_assert (index > 0);
8412
8413 /* Find the nth selected icon. */
8414 selection_count = 0;
8415 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8416 {
8417 icon = p->data;
8418 if (icon->is_selected)
8419 {
8420 if (++selection_count == index)
8421 {
8422 return icon;
8423 }
8424 }
8425 }
8426 return NULL;
8427}

8463
8470void
8471caja_icon_container_show_stretch_handles (CajaIconContainer *container)
8472{
8473 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
8474 CajaIcon *icon;
8475 guint initial_size;
8476
8477 icon = get_first_selected_icon (container);
8478 if (icon == NULL)
8479 {
8480 return;
8481 }
8482
8483 /* Check if it already has stretch handles. */
8484 details = container->details;
8485 if (details->stretch_icon == icon)
8486 {
8487 return;
8488 }
8489
8490 /* Get rid of the existing stretch handles and put them on the new icon. */
8491 if (details->stretch_icon != NULL)
8492 {
8493 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_show_stretch_handles
8494 (details->stretch_icon->item, FALSE);
8495 ungrab_stretch_icon (container);
8496 emit_stretch_ended (container, details->stretch_icon);
8497 }
8498 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_show_stretch_handles (icon->item, TRUE);
8499 details->stretch_icon = icon;
8500
8501 icon_get_size (container, icon, &initial_size);
8502
8503 /* only need to keep size in one dimension, since they are constrained to be the same */
8504 container->details->stretch_initial_x = icon->x;
8505 container->details->stretch_initial_y = icon->y;
8506 container->details->stretch_initial_size = initial_size;
8507
8508 emit_stretch_started (container, icon);
8509}

8517gboolean
8518caja_icon_container_has_stretch_handles (CajaIconContainer *container)
8519{
8520 CajaIcon *icon;
8521
8522 icon = get_first_selected_icon (container);
8523 if (icon == NULL)
8524 {
8525 return FALSE;
8526 }
8527
8528 return icon == container->details->stretch_icon;
8529}

8560void
8561caja_icon_container_unstretch (CajaIconContainer *container)

8572 icon->x, icon->y,
8573 1.0,
8574 FALSE, TRUE, TRUE);
8575 }

8578
8579static void
8580compute_stretch (StretchState *start,
8581 StretchState *current)
8582{
8583 gboolean right, bottom;
8584 int x_stretch, y_stretch;
8585
8586 /* FIXME bugzilla.gnome.org 45390: This doesn't correspond to
8587 * the way the handles are drawn.
8588 */
8589 /* Figure out which handle we are dragging. */
8590 right = start->pointer_x > start->icon_x + (int) start->icon_size / 2;
8591 bottom = start->pointer_y > start->icon_y + (int) start->icon_size / 2;
8592
8593 /* Figure out how big we should stretch. */
8594 x_stretch = start->pointer_x - current->pointer_x;
8595 y_stretch = start->pointer_y - current->pointer_y;
8596 if (right)
8597 {
8598 x_stretch = - x_stretch;
8599 }
8600 if (bottom)
8601 {
8602 y_stretch = - y_stretch;
8603 }
8604 current->icon_size = MAX ((int) start->icon_size + MIN (x_stretch, y_stretch),
8605 (int) CAJA_ICON_SIZE_SMALLEST);
8606
8607 /* Figure out where the corner of the icon should be. */
8608 current->icon_x = start->icon_x;
8609 if (!right)
8610 {
8611 current->icon_x += start->icon_size - current->icon_size;
8612 }
8613 current->icon_y = start->icon_y;
8614 if (!bottom)
8615 {
8616 current->icon_y += start->icon_size - current->icon_size;
8617 }
8618}

8647
8648/* Call to reset the scroll region only if the container is not empty,
8649 * to avoid having the flag linger until the next file is added.
8650 */
8651static void
8652reset_scroll_region_if_not_empty (CajaIconContainer *container)
8653{
8654 if (!caja_icon_container_is_empty (container))
8655 {
8656 caja_icon_container_reset_scroll_region (container);
8657 }
8658}
8659
8660/* Switch from automatic layout to manual or vice versa.
8661 * If we switch to manual layout, we restore the icon positions from the
8662 * last manual layout.
8663 */
8664void
8665caja_icon_container_set_auto_layout (CajaIconContainer *container,
8666 gboolean auto_layout)
8667{
8668 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
8669 g_return_if_fail (auto_layout == FALSE || auto_layout == TRUE);
8670
8671 if (container->details->auto_layout == auto_layout)
8672 {
8673 return;
8674 }
8675
8676 reset_scroll_region_if_not_empty (container);
8677 container->details->auto_layout = auto_layout;
8678
8679 if (!auto_layout)
8680 {
8681 reload_icon_positions (container, TRUE);
8682 caja_icon_container_freeze_icon_positions (container);
8683 }
8684
8685 redo_layout (container);
8686
8687 g_signal_emit (container, signals[LAYOUT_CHANGED], 0);
8688}
8689
8690/* Toggle the tighter layout boolean. */
8691void
8692caja_icon_container_set_tighter_layout (CajaIconContainer *container,
8693 gboolean tighter_layout)
8694{
8695 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
8696 g_return_if_fail (tighter_layout == FALSE || tighter_layout == TRUE);
8697
8698 if (container->details->tighter_layout == tighter_layout)
8699 {
8700 return;
8701 }
8702
8703 container->details->tighter_layout = tighter_layout;
8704
8705 if (container->details->auto_layout)
8706 {
8707 invalidate_label_sizes (container);
8708 redo_layout (container);
8709
8710 g_signal_emit (container, signals[LAYOUT_CHANGED], 0);
8711 }
8712 else
8713 {
8714 /* in manual layout, label sizes still change, even though
8715 * the icons don't move.
8716 */
8717 invalidate_label_sizes (container);
8718 caja_icon_container_request_update_all (container);
8719 }
8720}

8746static void
8747unschedule_align_icons (CajaIconContainer *container)

8750 {
8751 g_source_remove (container->details->align_idle_id);
8752 container->details->align_idle_id = 0;

8756static void
8757schedule_align_icons (CajaIconContainer *container)
8758{
8759 if (container->details->align_idle_id == 0
8760 && container->details->has_been_allocated)
8761 {
8762 container->details->align_idle_id = g_idle_add
8763 (align_icons_callback, container);
8764 }
8765}
8766
8767void
8768caja_icon_container_set_keep_aligned (CajaIconContainer *container,
8769 gboolean keep_aligned)
8770{
8771 if (container->details->keep_aligned != keep_aligned)
8772 {
8773 container->details->keep_aligned = keep_aligned;
8774
8775 if (keep_aligned && !container->details->auto_layout)
8776 {
8777 schedule_align_icons (container);
8778 }
8779 else
8780 {
8781 unschedule_align_icons (container);
8782 }
8783 }
8784}

8789{

8792 container->details->lock_icons_position = lock_icons_position;
8793}

8842
8843/* Switch from automatic to manual layout, freezing all the icons in their
8844 * current positions instead of restoring icon positions from the last manual
8845 * layout as set_auto_layout does.
8846 */
8847void
8848caja_icon_container_freeze_icon_positions (CajaIconContainer *container)
8849{
8850 gboolean changed;
8851 GList *p;
8852 CajaIcon *icon;
8853 CajaIconPosition position;
8854
8855 changed = container->details->auto_layout;
8856 container->details->auto_layout = FALSE;
8857
8858 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
8859 {
8860 icon = p->data;
8861
8862 position.x = icon->saved_ltr_x;
8863 position.y = icon->y;
8864 position.scale = icon->scale;
8865 g_signal_emit (container, signals[ICON_POSITION_CHANGED], 0,
8866 icon->data, &position);
8867 }
8868
8869 if (changed)
8870 {
8871 g_signal_emit (container, signals[LAYOUT_CHANGED], 0);
8872 }
8873}
8874
8875/* Re-sort, switching to automatic layout if it was in manual layout. */
8876void
8877caja_icon_container_sort (CajaIconContainer *container)
8878{
8879 gboolean changed;
8880
8881 changed = !container->details->auto_layout;
8882 container->details->auto_layout = TRUE;
8883
8884 reset_scroll_region_if_not_empty (container);
8885 redo_layout (container);
8886
8887 if (changed)
8888 {
8889 g_signal_emit (container, signals[LAYOUT_CHANGED], 0);
8890 }
8891}

8897
8898 return container->details->auto_layout;
8899}

8908
8909static void
8910pending_icon_to_rename_destroy_callback (CajaIconCanvasItem *item, CajaIconContainer *container)
8911{
8912 g_assert (container->details->pending_icon_to_rename != NULL);
8913 g_assert (container->details->pending_icon_to_rename->item == item);
8914 container->details->pending_icon_to_rename = NULL;
8915}
8916
8917static CajaIcon*
8918get_pending_icon_to_rename (CajaIconContainer *container)
8919{
8920 return container->details->pending_icon_to_rename;
8921}
8922
8923static void
8924set_pending_icon_to_rename (CajaIconContainer *container, CajaIcon *icon)
8925{
8926 CajaIcon *old_icon;
8927
8928 old_icon = container->details->pending_icon_to_rename;
8929
8930 if (icon == old_icon)
8931 {
8932 return;
8933 }
8934
8935 if (old_icon != NULL)
8936 {
8937 g_signal_handlers_disconnect_by_func
8938 (old_icon->item,
8939 G_CALLBACK (pending_icon_to_rename_destroy_callback),
8940 container);
8941 }
8942
8943 if (icon != NULL)
8944 {
8945 g_signal_connect (icon->item, "destroy",
8946 G_CALLBACK (pending_icon_to_rename_destroy_callback), container);
8947 }
8948
8949 container->details->pending_icon_to_rename = icon;
8950}
8951
8952static void
8953process_pending_icon_to_rename (CajaIconContainer *container)
8954{
8955 CajaIcon *pending_icon_to_rename;
8956
8957 pending_icon_to_rename = get_pending_icon_to_rename (container);
8958
8959 if (pending_icon_to_rename != NULL)
8960 {
8961 if (pending_icon_to_rename->is_selected && !has_multiple_selection (container))
8962 {
8963 caja_icon_container_start_renaming_selected_item (container, FALSE);
8964 }
8965 else
8966 {
8967 set_pending_icon_to_rename (container, NULL);
8968 }
8969 }
8970}
8971
8972static gboolean
8973is_renaming_pending (CajaIconContainer *container)
8974{
8975 return get_pending_icon_to_rename (container) != NULL;
8976}
8977
8978static gboolean
8979is_renaming (CajaIconContainer *container)
8980{
8981 return container->details->renaming;
8982}
8983
8992void
8993caja_icon_container_start_renaming_selected_item (CajaIconContainer *container,
8994 gboolean select_all)
8995{
8996 CajaIconContainerDetails *details;
8997 CajaIcon *icon;
8998 EelDRect icon_rect;
8999 EelDRect text_rect;
9000 PangoFontDescription *desc;
9001 const char *editable_text;
9002 int x, y, width;
9003 int start_offset, end_offset;
9004
9005 /* Check if it already in renaming mode, if so - select all */
9006 details = container->details;
9007 if (details->renaming)
9008 {
9009 eel_editable_label_select_region (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget),
9010 0,
9011 -1);
9012 return;
9013 }
9014
9015 /* Find selected icon */
9016 icon = get_first_selected_icon (container);
9017 if (icon == NULL)
9018 {
9019 return;
9020 }
9021
9022 g_assert (!has_multiple_selection (container));
9023
9024 if (!icon_is_positioned (icon))
9025 {
9026 set_pending_icon_to_rename (container, icon);
9027 return;
9028 }
9029
9030 set_pending_icon_to_rename (container, NULL);
9031
9032 /* Make a copy of the original editable text for a later compare */
9033 editable_text = caja_icon_canvas_item_get_editable_text (icon->item);
9034
9035 /* This could conceivably be NULL if a rename was triggered really early. */
9036 if (editable_text == NULL)
9037 {
9038 return;
9039 }
9040
9041 details->original_text = g_strdup (editable_text);
9042
9043 /* Freeze updates so files added while renaming don't cause rename to loose focus, bug #318373 */
9044 caja_icon_container_freeze_updates (container);
9045
9046 /* Create text renaming widget, if it hasn't been created already.
9047 * We deal with the broken icon text item widget by keeping it around
9048 * so its contents can still be cut and pasted as part of the clipboard
9049 */
9050 if (details->rename_widget == NULL)
9051 {
9052 details->rename_widget = eel_editable_label_new ("Test text");
9053 eel_editable_label_set_line_wrap (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget), TRUE);
9054 eel_editable_label_set_line_wrap_mode (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget), PANGO_WRAP_WORD_CHAR);
9055 eel_editable_label_set_draw_outline (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget), TRUE);
9056
9057 if (details->label_position != CAJA_ICON_LABEL_POSITION_BESIDE)
9058 {
9059 eel_editable_label_set_justify (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget), GTK_JUSTIFY_CENTER);
9060 }
9061
9062 gtk_widget_set_margin_start (details->rename_widget, 1);
9063 gtk_widget_set_margin_end (details->rename_widget, 1);
9064 gtk_widget_set_margin_top (details->rename_widget, 1);
9065 gtk_widget_set_margin_bottom (details->rename_widget, 1);
9066 gtk_layout_put (GTK_LAYOUT (container),
9067 details->rename_widget, 0, 0);
9068 }
9069
9070 /* Set the right font */
9071 if (details->font)
9072 {
9073 desc = pango_font_description_from_string (details->font);
9074 }
9075 else
9076 {
9077 PangoContext *context;
9078
9079 context = gtk_widget_get_pango_context (GTK_WIDGET (container));
9080 desc = pango_font_description_copy (pango_context_get_font_description (context));
9081 pango_font_description_set_size (desc,
9082 pango_font_description_get_size (desc) +
9083 container->details->font_size_table [container->details->zoom_level]);
9084 }
9085 eel_editable_label_set_font_description (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget),
9086 desc);
9087 pango_font_description_free (desc);
9088
9089 icon_rect = caja_icon_canvas_item_get_icon_rectangle (icon->item);
9090 text_rect = caja_icon_canvas_item_get_text_rectangle (icon->item, TRUE);
9091
9092 if (caja_icon_container_is_layout_vertical (container) &&
9093 container->details->label_position == CAJA_ICON_LABEL_POSITION_BESIDE)
9094 {
9095 /* for one-line editables, the width changes dynamically */
9096 width = -1;
9097 }
9098 else
9099 {
9100 width = caja_icon_canvas_item_get_max_text_width (icon->item);
9101 }
9102
9103 if (details->label_position == CAJA_ICON_LABEL_POSITION_BESIDE)
9104 {
9105 eel_canvas_w2c (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item)->canvas,
9106 text_rect.x0,
9107 text_rect.y0,
9108 &x, &y);
9109 }
9110 else
9111 {
9112 eel_canvas_w2c (EEL_CANVAS_ITEM (icon->item)->canvas,
9113 (icon_rect.x0 + icon_rect.x1) / 2,
9114 icon_rect.y1,
9115 &x, &y);
9116 x = x - width / 2 - 1;
9117 }
9118
9119 gtk_layout_move (GTK_LAYOUT (container),
9120 details->rename_widget,
9121 x, y);
9122
9123 gtk_widget_set_size_request (details->rename_widget,
9124 width, -1);
9125 eel_editable_label_set_text (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget),
9126 editable_text);
9127 if (select_all)
9128 {
9129 start_offset = 0;
9130 end_offset = -1;
9131 }
9132 else
9133 {
9134 eel_filename_get_rename_region (editable_text, &start_offset, &end_offset);
9135 }
9136 gtk_widget_show (details->rename_widget);
9137 gtk_widget_grab_focus (details->rename_widget);
9138
9139 eel_editable_label_select_region (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (details->rename_widget),
9140 start_offset,
9141 end_offset);
9142 g_signal_emit (container,
9143 signals[RENAMING_ICON], 0,
9144 GTK_EDITABLE (details->rename_widget));
9145
9146 caja_icon_container_update_icon (container, icon);
9147
9148 /* We are in renaming mode */
9149 details->renaming = TRUE;
9150 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_renaming (icon->item, TRUE);
9151}
9152
9153static void
9154end_renaming_mode (CajaIconContainer *container, gboolean commit)
9155{
9156 CajaIcon *icon;
9157
9158 set_pending_icon_to_rename (container, NULL);
9159
9160 icon = get_icon_being_renamed (container);
9161 if (icon == NULL)
9162 {
9163 return;
9164 }
9165
9166 /* We are not in renaming mode */
9167 container->details->renaming = FALSE;
9168 caja_icon_canvas_item_set_renaming (icon->item, FALSE);
9169
9170 caja_icon_container_unfreeze_updates (container);
9171
9172 if (commit)
9173 {
9174 set_pending_icon_to_reveal (container, icon);
9175 }
9176
9177 gtk_widget_grab_focus (GTK_WIDGET (container));
9178
9179 if (commit)
9180 {
9181 const char *changed_text;
9182
9183 /* Verify that text has been modified before signalling change. */
9184 changed_text = eel_editable_label_get_text (EEL_EDITABLE_LABEL (container->details->rename_widget));
9185 if (strcmp (container->details->original_text, changed_text) != 0)
9186 {
9187 AtkObject *accessible_icon;
9188
9189 g_signal_emit (container,
9190 signals[ICON_TEXT_CHANGED], 0,
9191 icon->data,
9192 changed_text);
9193
9194 accessible_icon = atk_gobject_accessible_for_object (G_OBJECT(icon->item));
9195 g_object_notify (G_OBJECT(accessible_icon), "accessible-name");
9196 }
9197 }
9198
9199 gtk_widget_hide (container->details->rename_widget);
9200
9201 g_free (container->details->original_text);
9202
9203}
9204
9205/* emit preview signal, called by the canvas item */
9206gboolean
9207caja_icon_container_emit_preview_signal (CajaIconContainer *icon_container,
9208 CajaIcon *icon,
9209 gboolean start_flag)
9210{
9211 gboolean result;
9212
9213 g_return_val_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (icon_container), FALSE);
9214 g_return_val_if_fail (icon != NULL, FALSE);
9215 g_return_val_if_fail (start_flag == FALSE || start_flag == TRUE, FALSE);
9216
9217 result = FALSE;
9218 g_signal_emit (icon_container,
9219 signals[PREVIEW], 0,
9220 icon->data,
9221 start_flag,
9222 &result);
9223
9224 return result;
9225}
9226
9227gboolean
9228caja_icon_container_has_stored_icon_positions (CajaIconContainer *container)
9229{
9230 GList *p;
9231 gboolean have_stored_position;
9232 CajaIconPosition position;
9233 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
9234
9235 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
9236 {
9237 icon = p->data;
9238
9239 have_stored_position = FALSE;
9240 g_signal_emit (container,
9241 signals[GET_STORED_ICON_POSITION], 0,
9242 icon->data,
9243 &position,
9244 &have_stored_position);
9245 if (have_stored_position)
9246 {
9247 return TRUE;
9248 }
9249 }
9250 return FALSE;
9251}

9338/* handle theme changes */
9339
9340void
9341caja_icon_container_set_font (CajaIconContainer *container,
9342 const char *font)
9343{
9344 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
9345

9347 {
9348 return;
9349 }

9352 container->details->font = g_strdup (font);

9356 gtk_widget_queue_draw (GTK_WIDGET (container));
9357}
9358
9359void
9360caja_icon_container_set_font_size_table (CajaIconContainer *container,
9361 const int font_size_table[CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGEST + 1])
9362{
9363 int old_font_size;
9364 int i;
9365
9366 g_return_if_fail (CAJA_IS_ICON_CONTAINER (container));
9367 g_return_if_fail (font_size_table != NULL);
9368
9369 old_font_size = container->details->font_size_table[container->details->zoom_level];
9370
9371 for (i = 0; i <= CAJA_ZOOM_LEVEL_LARGEST; i++)
9372 {
9373 if (container->details->font_size_table[i] != font_size_table[i])
9374 {
9375 container->details->font_size_table[i] = font_size_table[i];
9376 }
9377 }
9378
9379 if (old_font_size != container->details->font_size_table[container->details->zoom_level])
9380 {
9381 invalidate_labels (container);
9382 caja_icon_container_request_update_all (container);
9383 }
9384}

9399 klass = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER_GET_CLASS (container);
9400
9401 if (klass->get_icon_description)
9402 {
9403 return klass->get_icon_description (container, data);
9404 }
9405 else
9406 {
9407 return NULL;
9408 }
9409}

9486/* CajaIconContainerAccessible */
9487
9488static CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate *
9489accessible_get_priv (AtkObject *accessible)
9490{
9491 CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate *priv;

9494 accessible_private_data_quark);

9498
9499/* AtkAction interface */
9500
9501static gboolean
9502caja_icon_container_accessible_do_action (AtkAction *accessible, int i)
9503{
9504 GtkWidget *widget;
9505 CajaIconContainer *container;
9506 GList *selection;
9507
9508 g_return_val_if_fail (i < LAST_ACTION, FALSE);
9509
9510 widget = gtk_accessible_get_widget (GTK_ACCESSIBLE (accessible));
9511 if (!widget)
9512 {
9513 return FALSE;
9514 }
9515
9516 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (widget);
9517 switch (i)
9518 {
9519 case ACTION_ACTIVATE :
9520 selection = caja_icon_container_get_selection (container);
9521
9522 if (selection)
9523 {
9524 g_signal_emit_by_name (container, "activate", selection);
9525 g_list_free (selection);
9526 }
9527 break;
9528 case ACTION_MENU :
9529 handle_popups (container, NULL,"context_click_background");
9530 break;
9531 default :
9532 g_warning ("Invalid action passed to CajaIconContainerAccessible::do_action");
9533 return FALSE;
9534 }
9535 return TRUE;
9536}
9537
9538static int
9539caja_icon_container_accessible_get_n_actions (AtkAction *accessible)
9540{
9541 return LAST_ACTION;
9542}

9614static void
9615caja_icon_container_accessible_update_selection (AtkObject *accessible)
9616{
9617 CajaIconContainer *container;
9618 CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate *priv;
9619 GList *l;
9620 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
9621
9622 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (gtk_accessible_get_widget (GTK_ACCESSIBLE (accessible)));
9623
9624 priv = accessible_get_priv (accessible);
9625
9626 if (priv->selection)
9627 {
9628 g_list_free (priv->selection);
9629 priv->selection = NULL;
9630 }
9631
9632 for (l = container->details->icons; l != NULL; l = l->next)
9633 {
9634 icon = l->data;
9635 if (icon->is_selected)
9636 {
9637 priv->selection = g_list_prepend (priv->selection,
9638 icon);
9639 }
9640 }
9641
9642 priv->selection = g_list_reverse (priv->selection);
9643}

9646caja_icon_container_accessible_selection_changed_cb (CajaIconContainer *container,

9649 g_signal_emit_by_name (data, "selection_changed");

9652static void
9653caja_icon_container_accessible_icon_added_cb (CajaIconContainer *container,
9654 CajaIconData *icon_data,
9655 gpointer data)
9656{
9657 CajaIcon *icon;
9658
9659 // We don't want to emit children_changed signals during any type of load.
9660 if (container->details->is_loading || container->details->is_populating_container)
9661 return;
9662
9663 icon = g_hash_table_lookup (container->details->icon_set, icon_data);
9664 if (icon)
9665 {
9666 AtkObject *atk_parent;
9667 AtkObject *atk_child;
9668 int index;
9669
9670 atk_parent = ATK_OBJECT (data);
9671 atk_child = atk_gobject_accessible_for_object
9672 (G_OBJECT (icon->item));
9673 index = g_list_index (container->details->icons, icon);
9674
9675 g_signal_emit_by_name (atk_parent, "children_changed::add",
9676 index, atk_child, NULL);
9677 }
9678}

9681caja_icon_container_accessible_icon_removed_cb (CajaIconContainer *container,

9683 gpointer data)

9687 icon = g_hash_table_lookup (container->details->icon_set, icon_data);
9688 if (icon)
9689 {

9691 AtkObject *atk_child;
9692 int index;
9693
9694 atk_parent = ATK_OBJECT (data);
9695 atk_child = atk_gobject_accessible_for_object
9696 (G_OBJECT (icon->item));
9697 index = g_list_index (container->details->icons, icon);
9698
9699 g_signal_emit_by_name (atk_parent, "children_changed::remove",
9700 index, atk_child, NULL);
9701 }
9702}

9713 int i)
9714{
9715 GtkWidget *widget;
9716 CajaIconContainer *container;
9717 CajaIcon *icon;
9718
9719 widget = gtk_accessible_get_widget (GTK_ACCESSIBLE (accessible));
9720 if (!widget)
9721 {
9722 return FALSE;
9723 }
9724
9725 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (widget);
9726
9727 icon = g_list_nth_data (container->details->icons, i);
9728 if (icon)
9729 {

9734 icon->data);

9881void
9882caja_icon_container_widget_to_file_operation_position (CajaIconContainer *container,
9883 GdkPoint *position)
9884{
9885 double x, y;
9886
9887 g_return_if_fail (position != NULL);
9888
9889 x = position->x;
9890 y = position->y;
9891
9892 eel_canvas_window_to_world (EEL_CANVAS (container), x, y, &x, &y);
9893
9894 position->x = (int) x;
9895 position->y = (int) y;
9896
9897 /* ensure that we end up in the middle of the icon */
9898 position->x -= caja_get_icon_size_for_zoom_level (container->details->zoom_level) / 2;
9899 position->y -= caja_get_icon_size_for_zoom_level (container->details->zoom_level) / 2;
9900}

9937static AtkObject*
9938caja_icon_container_accessible_ref_child (AtkObject *accessible, int i)
9939{
9940 AtkObject *atk_object;
9941 CajaIconContainer *container;
9942 CajaIcon *icon;
9943 GtkWidget *widget;
9944
9945 widget = gtk_accessible_get_widget (GTK_ACCESSIBLE (accessible));
9946 if (!widget)
9947 {
9948 return NULL;
9949 }
9950
9951 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (widget);
9952
9953 icon = g_list_nth_data (container->details->icons, i);
9954 if (icon)

9957 g_object_ref (atk_object);

9967 atk_object = gtk_widget_get_accessible (container->details->rename_widget);
9968 g_object_ref (atk_object);

9977static void
9978caja_icon_container_accessible_initialize (AtkObject *accessible,
9979 gpointer data)
9980{
9981 CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate *priv;
9982
9983 if (ATK_OBJECT_CLASS (accessible_parent_class)->initialize)
9984 {
9985 ATK_OBJECT_CLASS (accessible_parent_class)->initialize (accessible, data);
9986 }
9987
9988 priv = g_new0 (CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate, 1);
9989 g_object_set_qdata (G_OBJECT (accessible),
9990 accessible_private_data_quark,
9991 priv);
9992
9993 if (GTK_IS_ACCESSIBLE (accessible))
9994 {
9995 CajaIconContainer *container;
9996
9997 caja_icon_container_accessible_update_selection
9998 (ATK_OBJECT (accessible));
9999
10000 container = CAJA_ICON_CONTAINER (gtk_accessible_get_widget (GTK_ACCESSIBLE (accessible)));
10001 g_signal_connect (G_OBJECT (container), "selection_changed",
10002 G_CALLBACK (caja_icon_container_accessible_selection_changed_cb),
10003 accessible);
10004 g_signal_connect (G_OBJECT (container), "icon_added",
10005 G_CALLBACK (caja_icon_container_accessible_icon_added_cb),
10006 accessible);
10007 g_signal_connect (G_OBJECT (container), "icon_removed",
10008 G_CALLBACK (caja_icon_container_accessible_icon_removed_cb),
10009 accessible);
10010 g_signal_connect (G_OBJECT (container), "cleared",
10011 G_CALLBACK (caja_icon_container_accessible_cleared_cb),
10012 accessible);
10013 }

10016static void
10017caja_icon_container_accessible_finalize (GObject *object)
10018{
10019 CajaIconContainerAccessiblePrivate *priv;
10020 int i;
10021
10022 priv = accessible_get_priv (ATK_OBJECT (object));
10023 if (priv->selection)
10024 {
10025 g_list_free (priv->selection);
10026 }
10027
10028 for (i = 0; i < LAST_ACTION; i++)
10029 {
10030 if (priv->action_descriptions[i])
10031 {
10032 g_free (priv->action_descriptions[i]);
10033 }
10034 }
10035
10036 g_free (priv);
10037
10038 G_OBJECT_CLASS (accessible_parent_class)->finalize (object);
10039}

10073static char *
10074check_compute_stretch (int icon_x, int icon_y, int icon_size,
10075 int start_pointer_x, int start_pointer_y,
10076 int end_pointer_x, int end_pointer_y)
10077{
10078 StretchState start, current;
10079
10080 start.icon_x = icon_x;
10081 start.icon_y = icon_y;
10082 start.icon_size = icon_size;
10083 start.pointer_x = start_pointer_x;
10084 start.pointer_y = start_pointer_y;
10085 current.pointer_x = end_pointer_x;
10086 current.pointer_y = end_pointer_y;
10087
10088 compute_stretch (&start, &current);
10089
10090 return g_strdup_printf ("%d,%d:%d",
10091 current.icon_x,
10092 current.icon_y,
10093 current.icon_size);
10094}

10181
10182static void
10183store_layout_timestamps_now (CajaIconContainer *container)
10184{
10185 GList *p;
10186 gboolean dummy;
10187 CajaIcon *icon = NULL;
10188
10189 container->details->layout_timestamp = time (NULL);
10190 g_signal_emit (container,
10191 signals[STORE_LAYOUT_TIMESTAMP], 0,
10192 NULL, &container->details->layout_timestamp, &dummy);
10193
10194 for (p = container->details->icons; p != NULL; p = p->next)
10195 {
10196 icon = p->data;
10197
10198 g_signal_emit (container,
10199 signals[STORE_LAYOUT_TIMESTAMP], 0,
10200 icon->data, &container->details->layout_timestamp, &dummy);
10201 }
10202}

10204void
10205caja_icon_container_end_loading (CajaIconContainer *container,
10206 gboolean all_icons_added)
10207{
10208 if (all_icons_added &&
10209 caja_icon_container_get_store_layout_timestamps (container))
10210 {
10211 if (container->details->new_icons == NULL)
10212 {
10213 store_layout_timestamps_now (container);
10214 }
10215 else
10216 {
10217 container->details->store_layout_timestamps_when_finishing_new_icons = TRUE;
10218 }
10219 }
10220}
